citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:45am on January
23, 2024. The inspector knocked on the door at the residence and was informed the licensee was not home and would
not be returning for several hours.
End Section
